<h2 id="18-safety-recommendations">18. Safety Recommendations</h2>
<p>For a companion bot, especially one with a personal identity/persona:</p>
<ol>
<li>Separate public and private modes.</li>
<li>Use privacy guardrails on every public Letta call.</li>
<li>Do not let the bot expose private owner context.</li>
<li>Rate-limit public replies.</li>
<li>Limit ambient comments to specific channels.</li>
<li>Let the bot choose to stay quiet.</li>
<li>Avoid sexual/romantic intensity with non-owner users.</li>
<li>Prefer short public replies.</li>
<li>Log errors locally, not in Discord.</li>
<li>Keep <code>.env</code> secrets out of Git.</li>
</ol>
