<h2 id="20-final-recommended-policy">20. Final Recommended Policy</h2>
<p>A good balanced AI companion Discord policy:</p>
<div class="code-card"><span class="code-lang">text</span><pre><code>The bot may talk publicly when summoned or when configured ambient rules allow it.
The bot may DM reports to users who requested reports.
The bot may only hold open-ended private DM conversations with the owner.
The bot must never reveal owner-private emotional, romantic, sexual, therapeutic, or personal context in public or to other users.
The bot should stay quiet when it has nothing meaningful to add.</code></pre></div>
<p>This gives people useful Discord features without turning the companion into an uncontrolled public version of a private relationship.</p>
